ai-mil3.2.9:1.2_0: “Venerable Sir, when you say ‘I am a swamp’, what is it that you don’t become a misery?”
ai-mil3.2.9:1.3_0: “It’s tireless, great king, that is present.”
ai-mil3.2.9:1.7_0: “Great king, those choices have passed, and perished. They have no result in the past, future or present.
ai-mil3.2.9:1.8_0: For those who have passed away, exception, he who was reborn there,
ai-mil3.2.9:1.9_0: For the sentient beings who have passed away, there is no sorrow or lamentation,
ai-mil3.2.9:1.10_0: Those sentient beings who are extinguished, and are extinguished there are no more.”
ai-mil3.2.9:4.1_0: The second sub-chapter on lying down is finished.
